2022/03/23/migrating-wordpress-e2e-tests-to-playwright/\">Migrating WordPress E2E tests to Playwright</a><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2022/03/07/the-performance-lab-plugin-has-been-released/\"></a><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2022/03/07/a-week-in-core-march-7-2022/\"></a><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2022/03/14/a-week-in-core-march-14-2022/\"></a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-community\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/community\">Community</a></h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/community/2022/03/03/2022-community-team-goals-summary/\"></a><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/community/2022/03/14/meetup-organizer-newsletter-march-2022/\">Meetup Organizer Newsletter: March 2022</a></li><li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/community/2022/03/23/return-to-events-blue-sky-thinking/\">Return to In-Person Events: Blue Sky Thinking</a></li><li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/community/2022/03/17/discussion-revisiting-in-person-regional-wordcamps/\">Discussion: Revisiting In-person Regional WordCamps</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-design\">Design</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/design/2022/03/28/design-share-mar-14-25/\">Design Share: Mar&nbsp;14–25</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-docs\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/docs\">Docs</a>:</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/docs/2022/03/23/working-on-wordpress-release-6-0-selecting-trac-tickets-for-devnotes/\"></a><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/docs/2022/03/28/onboarding-sessions-live/\">Onboarding sessions – live!</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-support-articles\">Support Articles:</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/article/submit-your-block-pattern-to-the-directory/\"></a><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/article/post-content-block/\">Post Content Block</a></li><li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/article/submit-your-block-pattern-to-the-directory/\"></a><a hr