s for OceanWP Users\" alt=\"Black Friday / Cyber Monday 2021: Best Deals for OceanWP Users\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">Black Friday and Cyber Monday Special Deals Await You! In this short but very sweet presentation, we&#8217;ve gathered all Black Friday and Cyber Monday deals offered by OceanWP partners. Upgrade hosting or get the tools you need to enhance your WordPress website to the max. We&#8217;ll start with &#8211; of course &#8211; yours truly, the [&#8230;]<p style=\"margin: 0!important;padding: 26px 0 0!important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/black-friday-cyber-monday-special-deals-2021/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #13aff0; border-radius: 30px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.4; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Read More</a></p></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Lior Zelering\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10985:\"<p style=\"display: block; padding: 0 0 24px; margin: 0 !important;\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/blog/black-friday-cyber-monday-special-deals-2021/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/oceanwp-black-friday-cyber-monday-deals.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"700\" title=\"Black Friday / Cyber Monday 2021: Best Deals for OceanWP Users\" alt=\"Black Friday / Cyber Monday 2021: Best Deals for OceanWP Users\" style=\"width: 100%!important;\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0 26px !important; margin: 0 !important;\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Black Friday and Cyber Monday Special Deals Await You!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this short but very sweet presentation, we&#8217;ve gathered all Black Friday and Cyber Monday deals offered by OceanWP partners. <strong>Upgrade hosting or get the tools you need to enhance your WordPress website to the max.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#8217;ll start with &#8211; of course &#8211; yours truly, the Ocean Core Extensions Bundle (wink wink).</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1 Ocean Core Extensions Bundle &#8211; The Ultimate Black Friday / Cyber Monday Sale Bash</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Get the Ocean Core Extensions Bundle during the <strong><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/core-extensions-bundle/\">Black Friday / Cyber Monday Ultimate Sale Bash and save up to 55%!</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Taste the power of freedom with almost endless possibilities</strong>. Enhance your website with with 20+ extensions, including the latest Ocean Gutenberg Blocks plugin, and get access to ALL <a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/demos/\">WordPress website templates (demos)</a>. If you were considering a lifetime plan, don&#8217;t miss this limited offer <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.1.0/72x72/1f609.png\" alt=\"😉\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/core-extensions-bundle/\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/oceanwp-black-friday-2021.png\" alt=\"OceanWP Black Friday Cyber Monday promo banner\" class=\"wp-image-624049\" width=\"525\" height=\"525\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/oceanwp-black-friday-2021.png 700w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/oceanwp-black-friday-2021-300x300.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/oceanwp-black-friday-2021-150x150.png 150w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/oceanwp-black-friday-2021-128x128.png 128w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/oceanwp-black-friday-2021-256x256.png 256w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sale Start Date</strong>: November 18th 2021.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sale End Date:</strong> December 3rd 2021.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/core-extensions-bundle/\">All discounts calculated automatically at the checkout page</a>. For all other purchase stops, use the promo code: <strong>BFCM2021</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>In case you&#8217;d like to renew or upgrade your current license using this promotion, you can do that too! If you have any questions about specific details of your renewal / upgrade, make sure to send us a ticket.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2 Cloudways Offers 40% OFF On All Hosting Plans</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cloudways.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Cloudways</strong></a> is the leading cloud-based hosting platform popular for its scalability, user-friendliness, and impeccable customer support. It offers the users to pick their preferred platform from DigitalOcean, Linode, VULTR, Google Cloud Platform, and AWS.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Providing the best hosting solutions, this Black Friday, <strong>Cloudways offers AMAZING discounts and deals for its customers</strong> to begin their digital journey. Get started with a <strong><a href=\"https://platform.cloudways.com/signup?coupon=BFCM2021\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">FLAT 40% DISCOUNT for four months straight</a>!</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https://platform.cloudways.com/signup?coupon=BFCM2021\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/cloudways-black-friday-cyber-monday-2021-1024x341.jpg\" alt=\"Cloudways Black Friday Cyber Monday promo banner\" class=\"wp-image-624207\" width=\"768\" height=\"256\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/cloudways-black-friday-cyber-monday-2021-1024x341.jpg 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/cloudways-black-friday-cyber-monday-2021-300x100.jpg 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/cloudways-black-friday-cyber-monday-2021-768x256.jpg 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/cloudways-black-friday-cyber-monday-2021.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sale Start Date</strong>: November 23rd 2021.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sale End Date:</strong> December 1st 2021.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Promo Code:</strong> BFCM2021 or get the <strong><a href=\"https://platform.cloudways.com/signup?coupon=BFCM2021\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">40% OFF for 4 Months on all hosting plans immediately</a></strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All new users can take advantage of the discount.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3 Crocoblock &#8211; Black Friday &amp; Cyber Monday &#8211; Get up to 40% OFF</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This Black Friday, you can<strong> <a href=\"https://crocoblock.com/?ref=3457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">grab up to 40% discounts on Crocoblock products</a></strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yearly or Lifetime subscriptions will give you access to 20 JetPlugins, 12 dynamic templates, 50 interactive popups, and 47 design templates. Furthermore, you get updates and support.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Crocoblock is known as a top-rated Elementor addons provider, but it also has WordPress plugins for Gutenberg. So, you get everything you need for dynamic website building.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/300x600-Crocoblock-Black-Friday-2021.jpg\" alt=\"Crocoblock Black Friday Cyber Monday promo banner\" class=\"wp-image-624196\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https://crocoblock.com/?ref=3457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/C